ots |publisher=[[Pantheon Books]] |isbn=0-394-53890-0 }} *{{cite book |author=Timothy Ferris |year=1980 |title=Galaxies |publisher=[[Sierra Club Books]] |isbn=978-0-87156-273-9 }} *{{cite book |author=Carl Sagan, Frank D. Drake, Ann Druyan, Timothy Ferris, Jon Lomberg, and Linda Salzman Sagan |year=1978 |title=Murmurs of Earth: The Voyager Interstellar Record |publisher=[[Random House]] |isbn=978-0-345-31536-6 }}
